title: Urban Meyer on Players He's Coached, Culture & Competitiveness
itunes:title: Urban Meyer on Players He's Coached, Culture & Competitiveness
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks are back with a new episode. To start off, the guys are joined by former Ohio State head football coach Urban Meyer, as he talks about his thoughts on Michael Jordan, former Ohio State pass rushers and cornerbacks he's coached, competitiveness, and much more (2:58). After that, the pair react to the main points from the interview and expand on what they learned from it (25:50).
